professional cooperation, which over time has developed to a close friendship.

I have always experienced John as 100% company man. At all times focused, with his good analytic sense, professionalism, understanding of what it takes, without going to far, and his sense of good business acumen, to carry out company’s best interests. Skills he highly utilizes to achieve the best results.

John is very dedicated, energetic, industrious and hardworking. He is always there when an extra effort is needed. He always goes a step further.

John is very well liked among his colleagues and as chief. He’s engaged in the wellbeing of his employees and meets them with great confidence and high degree of freedom. It’s a pleasure to work with, and for John Walsh.See moreSee lessJohn has strong skills in inventory management, logistics, purchasing, product management and forecasting. He leads accurately and consistently these areas and John does not accept failure or fluctuation in the areas which are under his responsibility.
John takes rapid action and pursue own tasks all the way to the end. He is very precise and direct in his communication and thereby comes rapidly to a solution.
